== TitanChat

TitanChat, a chat management plugin for Bukkit.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Features

* Create new channels without editing config
* Ban players from channels
* Kick players from channels
* Add Admins to administrate channels
* Use colour codes on channels if not restricted

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Functions

* Manages chat

